\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Harrowby Street. Docks. Docks. Mm, Docks, Cardiff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And you're married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 The year of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 1914. 10th of February.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And the year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 1890.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 In George Street Docks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh about - I think my mother was there about two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where did you go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12462136\charrsid1668751 To E}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 leanor Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Still in the Docks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, just over the bridge here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know why they moved then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh I've no idea, well she was living - my grandmother had a sh
op - grandfather had a shop there, well they lived - a greengrocery shop - and my mother was living there - with them. Then they went next door, next door belonged to my grandfather, they - they went in there to live.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How long did you live there then in Eleanor Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh in Eleanor Street - up 'til the time I was married but my mother lived there oh about fifty-seven, fifty-eight years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You moved then when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where did you move then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 To Stewart Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Still in the Docks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How long did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Six months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 To France.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You were called up then, where did you go to live when you came out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 My wife went - was home - up home in her mother's up
 at Pontypool. And then I got lodgings down here until we found a place. Then we - bought a little house in - Grangestone, Bromfield Street. We sold that. And come over here again, to the Windsor Esplanade. We were there - how long was we there, twelve or
 eighteen months - then we went to - we had a house then in Eleanor Street. House of our own like. We were there 'til we come over here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When did you come here? You've been here about thirty-six years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh my God. One - two, three, four, five. Five sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Any brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
One, two, three, four - six brothers wasn't it. There was twins then. One died, a baby. And the other one lived 'til she was fifty didn't she. Nellie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would that be about two years younger than Tom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh no, they were - there was a little gap between them, about four or five years
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That would be about 1900?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Somewhere like that I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Is Lily alive now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, she's dead now. Jinny. She's still alive. Then there was Bob, Robert.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would Jinny be about two years younger than the twins?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And Robert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh he was a bit younger. He was about three - three or four years younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 So that was about 1905. Tom we 
worked out was born in 1896. George 1894. Susan 1892. And yourself in 1890. And then you had an older step-brother 1884. And step-sister, 1880?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm. Mm. Mm hm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That's all of them is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Your father was about twenty-three when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 He was bred and born in the Docks here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 A boatman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did he have another job before that or after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. Oh after, he - went up piloting after boating. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did he ever do any casual or part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Those are the only jobs he had until he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That's right.
