\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, or my mother, one or other.
