\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm. And your pare
nt - your grandparents had boats there, you - no trouble to get aboard of one of them or - go and scull around in the small boat you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you remember any outings with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, went to St Pagans once. My mother had relatives there a
nd we - went to see them, my father and mother and - me. And they took me. Well we called it outing because I was playing with the kids in the field there. That's only - but any other outings you had to - it would be yourself.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about Bank Holidays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
Didn't make much difference. When Campbell's boats were running in them days - the old horse trams were running you know, and the people used to get off, carrying their bags or portmanteaux, we used to say, carry your bag sir? We use
d to carry them from the tram to the - pontoon, and get a penny or something. That's holiday - time. Earning a few coppers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That was your Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, getting yourself a few coppers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You enjoyed that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well aye. You'd have enough money to go to the Empire in the night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Who would go to the Empire with you,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh all the other boys. All the boys playing about like, Aye, we could - good times, you could always fiddle a few coppers down here.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What, before I was married? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When you were a little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. Only go away - used to go to Port Talbot. To my aunt's down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When you were in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When would you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 In the summer holidays. Used to have a farm like down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How many of you would go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Only me. And - the next fortnight my sister go down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would they all go, would all the children go in turn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, not all of 'em, they were - as we were getting older th
ey - of course their families were getting bigger. And Barry, Barry Island, used to down there, I - uncle a pilot down there. I used to go down there sometimes for a week.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you go on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 A week there did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, have a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you go every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh no, not every year. Well - maybe over Whitsuntide. Then in the summer holiday you see got to Port Talbot like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What would you do there, when you were away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh play about with the other kids. We were only kiddies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you go on your own mostly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye. Yes. Sometimes - your sisters or them would go on their own like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Who would take you, how would you get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 By train. Well it was no trouble going to Port Talbot. Get out at the station, you - you was in Grove Place in two seconds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about going to Barry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No trouble there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You'd go on your own, your mother and father wouldn't take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How did you spend Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
Well I used to - there was a grocer down there in Market Street, Davis, I used to go around - with the - help the other boy with the groceries, you know, taking them down. Used to have eighteen pence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 So you had a little part time job really?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How did you get that, how did you hear about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well, my mother used to deal there, a good customer with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What hours would you have to work on a Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh when - no particular hours, you go in the morning about 
- ten o'clock, between nine and ten. Oh - it - you wasn't at it all the time like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Just taking groceries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, somebody's groceries around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You'd hang around the shop would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When would you finish then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh finish after dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And you had eighteen pence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you think that was fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Very good I think. It was a lot of money then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Of course I did. I give it - used to give it to her all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What she used to spend it on, well - know we always used to have plenty of sweets there for Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How did you get on with the other people there in the shop and the grocer himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well there 
was only - two in the shop. Wasn't a big shop, little shop. All right. No interference. Used to dabble our hand in the - in the tube now and again and take apple out.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well - nothing happened, you would - you wouldn't eat it in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about Sundays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
Oh well - it's all according to how things were. Sometimes you'd go to the - St Stevens church. Sometimes you go to the Baptist chapel. And the Plymouth Brethren. All according. It was just for - ab
out couple of weeks before Whitsun you - lets go so and so and so and so. Might go in to Sally Whitsun. Of course you'd all present yourself this Sunday afternoon for Sunday school. If their treat was Sunday of course you was in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 And then you'd go on the trip?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, we got on the - Whitsun treat then. But we - you wasn't tied to any - tied to no - denomination like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You'd go Sunday afternoon would you, how would you spend the rest of Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh, playing about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you have different clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh aye, proper Sunday clothes. And they was - they had to be clean when we took them off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You couldn't play in those clothes could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh no. Oh the Sunday suit and that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you play games on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 We had plenty to play with down here, plenty of - all - messing about with the boats you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You'd have to change your clothes though would you to go and a play like that on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well - they never interfered as long as you didn't do no damage.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did they go to a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. I never known 'em go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you go to a Sunday school or not, you didn't go regularly anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You went to different ones when the trips and things were coming up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 We did - aye. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about those Sunday school outings, how many did you manage to go on like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well - went to quite a few. They only had them Whitsun time you 
know, Whitsun treat. We'd have a couple of - coal carts mostly, swept out with - side - wooden sides put on 'em and seat - benches - bits of wood across to sit on. Take you to St. Pagans or - Sophia Gardens or somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you go to Sully?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How would you get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 In the - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Were there any other social activities organized by the church or chapel that you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, I wasn't a great -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about any clubs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Was grace said at meals at your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Grace, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh say your prayers, had to kneel down by the bed.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Not to my knowledge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh Conservative. Very Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Why do you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well, he always used to say to me, always support the bridge that carries you over. Well they were the 
people with the cash weren't they. They had the ways and means of - doing things and making work for you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about your mother, did she have a big interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. No politics, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know what her views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Don't know what her views was any particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you remember your father or mother voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh good God I - they used to vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know what party they'd voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Ah well that's - a man would be a fool to tell his employer what it was wouldn't he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure? To vote for a particular party?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, none whatever. No. Clear of the - place or - whoever he was. You had to vote for him didn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Was that like that down here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. No. Everybody was freebooters down here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Was your father a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 He's a member of the Conservative club I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I was going to ask you if he belonged to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes, the Conservative Club. Same as me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did he go a lot, did he go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh when he had a - night off like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your mother go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about the pubs then, did your father go to pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh aye. He wasn't a teetotaler by any means.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would he go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When he was at - when he had time off, he'd go and have a drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your mother go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
No. Although she wasn't a teetotaller mind. About half past - eleven or twelve o'clock every morning go over and get her half a pint of beer. She'd have bread and cheese and - snack like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would she go and get it or would you get it for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh, one of us'd have to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That would be every morning would it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well - practically every morning. And when the washerwoman was there you got a pint that d
ay. And the pair of 'em'd sit down and have bread and cheese and - glass of beer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 For elevenses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm. And if - there was a heavy day you'd have a go and turn the mangle. To - help out like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You remember doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh God, I - hundreds of times. Caught my fingers in it once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Was it bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes, there's a mark now still on the - well, very near took the top of that finger off, the mark's still there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You can have a nasty accident with them can't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you do that when you were in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 While I was going to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you do it in the holiday time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well any time. Oh God, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Tell me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I wouldn't go to school at all if I could help it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I didn't like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you stay home often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 As often as possible. Mitching.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That's why you were there to turn the mangle is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh no, you - you didn't come in 'til after school hours, if you were mitching.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You didn't show?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, not likely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You used to go out did you, pretend you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Pretend to go to school. Then up the pierhead then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you ever get caught?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well, you - might have a tanning when you got in school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would many of you do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
Oh Lord, aye. Half the blooming school down here. Well they give you a job, washing out inkwells or - something, some - sort of punishment you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you stay away a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 As often as possible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How often would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh - two or three days a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
You were saying your father was a member of the Conservative Club, but you don't know if he was actually a member of the Conservative party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. He never had time to mess about like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You don't remember him working for one of the parties at an election or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Or your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Not doing any work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh, they might - go - go to the Empire together or - theatre or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. Only had her family, all her young family see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, not as I'm aware of really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You mentioned she would go to the Empire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye, well that's only a night isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would she go often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Go with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Your father had to work with the tides?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 So he didn't come home a regular time did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. No. But sometimes when he would go off a bit quiet you know - you could take a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh - not two I don't think.
