\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Aye. All the boys did. All in them days of course. It's different - different t
oday you see. The - they don't let 'em down canal here, used to run down in a basin. There was always water there. And you could always go in swimming there see.
