\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Tinned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you have tinned fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well - we preferred the bottled fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you have dried fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Only - apricots. Aye, prunes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 There'd be no livestock because you had no garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Every day. Well we had fish like. Mm. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Tinned meat? Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I think there was corned beef about wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes, oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you have any extra meat obtained from poaching or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did your wife ever have to go short so that you could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you need to have larger helpings of food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 It's all according how you felt. No, I think - you - got used to that sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Can you remember anything you did with your wife on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh never made much difference did it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You'd have to work on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm. Probably work one tide of a Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I had a mandolin once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did she play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 A couple of notes on it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did either of you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you ever make music together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What, sing together? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Were there any books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh I used to read a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Always been the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Sometimes, all according.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where would you get the books from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh I used to get a lot from - the Seamen's Mission, and the library.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You belonged to the library did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did Mrs Stoodley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you read aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What did you do on Bank Holidays in those days, would you have to work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 We didn't - it - it - you work one tide, instead of working the two tides in the twenty-four hours you'd work one of 'em in the daytime.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you do anything special on the holiday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh we might go - nice fine day go up - Roath Park or somewhere didn't we. Or go to Penarth or down Barry Island or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you ever go away on a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh yes. Couple of times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 For how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 A week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, we didn't go regularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You couldn't go because you were working then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, but - after the war. We didn't go regularly. We'd have a see in Wessex or - Ilfracombe. Or we'd go up London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about Saturdays in those days after you were married, how would you spend Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh might go - might go shopping together. Go to the pictures - the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
I never went to church. I went a couple of times to - the Seventh Day Adventist didn't we. Pastor Jones. Come home from there and then go to club.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you think it wrong to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 How do you mean wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Some people think it's wrong to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, you've got to get your - no matter what day it is you've got to get your living haven't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about enjoying yourself, did you think it wrong to enjoy yourself on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 I couldn't see any wrong in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you think it didn't matter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No, I see no wrong in enjoying yourself Sunday. As long as you didn't get drunk or cause a riot or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You mentioned that your wife went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where would she go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 To the - Church of England wasn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you say grace at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Would you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Not really, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Just before the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 You mentioned earlier that you were Conservative?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Why did you think that, why were you that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 
Well - you can see what's come today - with this trade unionism, they're ruling the country, not the Government. Now they're putting the country in a state of anarchy to my opinion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What did you think about in 1914, what was your view then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well the - of course it was a - a Liberal Government in then wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 The Labour party hadn't really come to the fore had it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well now of
 course the Liberal Government was good government, it's - practically the same as the Conservative Government is today. Yes. Not - much different. None of this Communism in it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Why do you think how were Conservative then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well always support the bridge that carries you over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 What about Mrs Stoodley, would she be interested in politics then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Do you know what her views were then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well Conservative I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Why do you think she was Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Well she used to go around - going round knocking the doors for the candidates down here. Asking them to go and give their vote and that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 So she would work for the Conservative party at elections?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Was she a member of the Conservative party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Yes. Yes.
