\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14556438 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1907356 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13532555\charrsid1668751 Oh might go to the pictures or - somewhere like you know. Theatre.
